Step 1: Draw a large rounded head at the top center of your page.
Step 2: Add two large floppy ears on each side of the head, shaped like big semi-circles.
Step 3: Draw a long curved trunk extending down from the center of the head, tapering towards the end.
Step 4: Add two big friendly eyes on the upper part of the head, with small dots inside for pupils.
Step 5: Draw a rounded body shape below the head, connecting seamlessly to the bottom of the trunk.
Step 6: Add four thick, sturdy legs extending down from the body, with rounded feet at the bottom of each leg.
Step 7: Draw a small, curved tail at the back of the body, with a tuft at the end for added character.